https://reviews.apache.org/api/review-requests/40098/reviews/
This will give all the reviews

Where to find all the paths?

https://reviews.apache.org/api/review-requests/40253/diffs
This will give all the revision numbers

https://reviews.apache.org/api/review-requests/40253/diffs/2/files/
this will give the file path